description:
Today on the show we had our guys and host of the Earn Your Leisure podcast and 19 Keys stopped by where they spoke about diversifying your education, tokenomics, regulating crypto and more. Also, Charalamagne gave a well derserved "Donkey of the Day" to the police that arrested Black Panther director Ryan Coogler and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
